Package banking

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountInformation
    The static members of this class incorporate information about accounts offered by the bank.
    Balances
    Representation for customer's current account balances as returned by the bank.
    Card
    Representation for customer's ATM card
    Message
    Representations of a message from the ATM to the bank.
    Money
    Representation for money amounts
    Receipt
    Abstract base class for representation of a receipt to be printed.
    Status
    Abstract base class for representation of various status codes returned by bank for a transaction.
